POST-DEPLOYMENT STEPS

  1. Push homepage:
     $ git push origin main

  2. Schedule CRON:
     $ supabase functions schedule refresh-safety-summary "0 6 * * *"

  3. Verify:
     $ npm run verify:all

  4. Monitor:
     Follow docs/POST_LAUNCH_MONITORING.md

